What is final, finally and finalize?
The final keyword is a non access modifier used for classes, attributes and methods. Finally defines a block of code to run when the try, except that means it can be useful to close objects and clean up resources,
Finalize is a method of the Object class that is used to perform clean up activity before destroying any objects.
What is a constructor ?
A constructor in java is similar that is invoked when an object of the class is created.
Can we have multiple constructors in a class?
Yes we can have many constructors in a class that differ in the number or type of the parameter.
If we don't have a constructor declared, what is called during the object creation?
A default constructor is created only when there is no declared any constructor in the code.
What is "this" keyword in java ?
"This" keyword in Java is a reference variable that refers to the current object of a method or a constructor.
What is "super" keyword in java? How many possible way can you use?
The super keyword in java is a reference variable that is used to refer to parent class objects.
